ason why I stopped\npracticing with you.$k\n$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$Eキメ,汗|Y-yes... I'm really sorry...$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wa$E怒,汗|It's fine. We were both younger.$k$pI'm leaving, then.$k\n$Wsタクミ|$Wd$w0|$Wsカザハナ|$Wa$E怒,|P-Prince Takumi...\nH-hmm... so that was why...$k
